       The design of LTGOLD and LTPRO allows the user to  electronically
       translate written documents from English to Russian.  The program
       is designed for ease of use and speed. Although the program has a
       large built in dictionary, it is recommended that you have a good
       working knowledge of both English and Russian.  LTGOLD,  as  with
       other translation programs,  is not designed to replace the human
       translator,  but to  assist  them  in  turning  out  professional
       translations, several  times faster than ever before.  Even users
       with a minimum knowledge of Russian or  English  can  communicate
       effectively with people who know only one of the two languages.


                 1.0 SYSTEM HARDWARE AND SOFTWARE REQUIREMENTS


         The minimum  software  and  hardware  required  for LTGOLD to
         function correctly on your computer:


                   Computer: IBM XT, or compatible
                   Operating System: DOS 3.3 or higher
                   Memory 640 Kb.
		   EGA, VGA, SVGA card.
                   Hard Drive: 3 megabytes Free space
                   Software: Memory resident Cyrillic screen driver


                   A mouse is also recommended.


      ┌───────────────────────────  NOTE ───────────────────────────────┐
      │    LTGOLD was developed to run on IBM or fully compatible PC's  │
      │    including the XT, AT, 386, 486, PS/2, and laptops.   LTGOLD  │
      │    is compatible with DOS version 3.3 or higher.                │
      └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘


