                            5.0 DISTRIBUTION FILES

          The programs included in the distribution are:


   INSTALL .EXE       Installation Program
   INSTALLE.HLP       Installation English help text
   INSTALLR.HLP       Installation Russian help text
   README  .ENG       English Installation document
   README  .CYR       Russian Installation document
   QUESTION.ENG       Questions and Answers frequently asked
   NEWLTGE .DOC       English document with latest update notes
   NEWLTGR .DOC       Russian document with latest update notes
   ARD     .COM       Russian Screen Driver (try first)
   RKVGA   .COM       Russian Screen Driver (try second)
   RKA     .COM       Russian Screen Driver (try third)
   LTG     .EXE       Archive program including:
            LTGOLD  .EXE     Main LTGOLD program
            LTPRO   .EXE     Main LTPRO program
            LTPRO   .HLP     Help file for LTPRO (LTPRO/? to activate)
            LTGCMD  .HLP     Commands for LTGOLD (LTGOLD/? to activate)
            LTGOLDE .HLP     English help text for LTGOLD
            LTGOLDR .HLP     Russian help text for LTGOLD
            BASE    .DIC     Main English/Russian Dictionary
            BASE    .RUS     Main Russian Dictionary
            COMPUTER.DIC     Computer Dictionary
            BUSINESS.DIC     Business Dictionary
            LTPW5_0 .GLY     Macro for Word 5.0
            LTPW5_5 .GLY     Macro for Word 5.5
            LTPRO   .MAC     Macro for Multi-Edit
	    LTPRO   .SRC     Macro source for Multi-Edit
	    LTDOC   .DOC     Macro for WinWord 2.0
	    LTSELECT.DOC     Macro for WinWord 2.0
	    LTINSERT.DOC     Macro for WinWord 2.0
	    LT*     .PIF     PIF files for running LTGOLD under Windows 3.1
	    LT*     .ICO     Icons for running LTGOLD under Windows 3.1
            LTGOLD  .IDS     Words you do not want to translate
            DEMO    .TXT     Sample contract for translation
            LTATGGTA.EXE     Self-extracting communication files
            911     .EXE     Self-extracting Dictionary program including:
                     SUPPORT .EXE   Dictionary update program
                     SUPPORT .ENG   English documentation on SUPPORT.EXE
                     SUPPORT .CYR   Russian documentation on SUPPORT.EXE
                     APPENDIX.ENG   English Dictionary documentation
                     APPENDIX.CYR   Russian Dictionary documentation
                     USER    .DIC   User Dictionary (no entries)


