                           6.0 OPERATIONAL WARNINGS

         6.1 When   installing   LTGOLD   be  sure  your  computer  is
             configured in the same way  as  when  you  will  run  the
             program.  Changes in the system configuration may require
             reinstalling the program.


         6.2 LTGOLD does not allow for the copying  of  program  files
             from one computer to another.  An error will be displayed
             if the files are moved to another  computer  without  the
             complete installation process.


         6.3 Always   back   up   your  distribution  diskette  before
             installing the program.  You must use DISKCOPY (from your
             DOS  distribution  diskette)  to back up the distribution
             diskette.

         6.4 Please honor our Copyright and do not distribute  LTGOLD.
             The  money  we  receive  is  used  to further develop the
             product and dictionaries.


               WE HOPE YOU HAVE FUN WORKING AND PLAYING WITH LTGOLD
